page.title: 14WHERE WE LIVE 2
page.content: On the west side of Prince Regent's Lane at the junction of Victoria Dock Road is Cundy Park. As you walk northwards you find the Prince of Wales Public House and Cundy Road where there are eight shops; a newsagent, chemist, hairdresser, butcher,post office, butcher, grocer and betting office. Further north in Prince Regent's Lane is Berwick Road where you will find St. Joachim's Primary School, Custom House Working Men's Club and St. Anne's Parish Hall. Moving north again you arrive at the Shipman Youth Centre. Next you find a dry cleaners, a fish and chip shop and a launderette. Further north there are a grocer's, a Chinese take-away, an empty shop and a betting office.
